'''Psi-Tech''' is the [[Tho'ra Clan]]'s family of psionic devices designed to support, attune, and defend a single operator's [[Psi Field]]. The core line consists of three modules — the [[Psi Stabilizer]], the [[Psi Harmonizer]], and the [[Psi Defender]] — carried in the [[HelmKit]] psi-bay and grounded in the field theory laid out in [[Scientific Foundations of Psionics]].

Psi-Tech is one of the [[Tho'ra Clan|Clan's]] two technological mission pillars (the other being [[Magnetogravitics|magnetogravitic propulsion]] / the [[Magneto Speeder]] line).

== The Triad ==

{| class="wikitable"
! Module !! Function !! Doctrinal Role
|-
| [[Psi Stabilizer]] || User-controlled cognitive & emotional stabilization || Keeps you steady
|-
| [[Psi Harmonizer]] || Astrological-attunement brain entrainment || Keeps you in tune
|-
| [[Psi Defender]] || Defensive shield against psionic weapons & psychic attack || Keeps you safe
